<p>
  <span class="nym">Carla</span>
  <span class="gen">f.</span>
  
  <span class="etym">Fem. of <a class="nym" href="Charles">Charles</a>.
  </span>
  
</p>
  
  
<div class="def">
  <p>The name was never common in any context, and the diminutive forms were more popular than the radiconym.</p>
</div>
  


